    "The bulk G (1) = 2 1-form symmetry is now fractionalized to non-invertible (1-form) symmetry on the world-volume of O 3 because of the last fusion rule in (70).",
    "The localized symmetry is stillG (1) O 3 = 2, (109)generated by D (-)1, so we can regard Ising category as a categorical extension of G (1) = 2 by G (1) O 3 = 2, writing an analog of ( 108)\"0 -→ G (1) O 3 = 2 -→ G (1) ind-loc = Ising -→ G (1) = 2 -→ 0\".",
    "(110) Non-genuine generalized chargesSo far we considered only genuine q-charges.",
    "As we will discuss now, non-genuine charges arise naturally in field theories and require an extension, to include a higher-categorical structure.",
    "The summary of this structure can be found in statement 1.5."
